37
00:07:02,164 --> 00:07:03,832
- Are you alright?
- Yes, thank you.

38
00:07:03,958 --> 00:07:05,959
- Is everything alright?
- I said: Yes!

39
00:07:06,043 --> 00:07:07,794
Are you okay, Brummer?

40
00:07:07,837 --> 00:07:11,214
- I didn't hurt myself.
- Your back, ankle?

41
00:07:11,298 --> 00:07:15,343
- I'm not hurt at all!
- Are you sure?

42
00:07:15,469 --> 00:07:17,971
Please, try not to move around.

43
