48
00:08:56,320 --> 00:08:59,906
Not me, Lord, please.

49
00:08:59,949 --> 00:09:01,824
Not me.

50
00:09:01,951 --> 00:09:04,827
Not me, Lord, please.

51
00:09:04,954 --> 00:09:07,830
Not me, Lord.

52
00:09:18,342 --> 00:09:20,843
No, I said no!

53
00:09:46,328 --> 00:09:48,204
Gregori.

54
00:09:48,247 --> 00:09:50,123
Bikila.

55
00:09:51,625 --> 00:09:53,126
Aguilar.

56
00:09:55,004 --> 00:09:55,548
Gregori.

57
00:10:04,138 --> 00:10:07,390
- Where does Gregori stand?
- 13.

58
00:10:07,474 --> 00:10:09,517
Gregori 18, Bikila 11.

59
00:10:10,477 --> 00:10:12,729
- Bikila.
- Gregori 21.

60
00:10:12,771 --> 00:10:15,773
- Aguilar 18.
- Gregori and Bikila 15.

61
00:10:15,899 --> 00:10:17,650
Bikila.

62
00:10:20,779 --> 00:10:23,239
- Aguilar.
- Just a moment!

63
00:10:23,282 --> 00:10:25,033
Gregori.

64
00:10:25,117 --> 00:10:26,534
Lucci.

65
00:10:26,660 --> 00:10:30,288
The smoke's black,
the Pope still hasn't been elected.

66
00:10:30,414 --> 00:10:32,874
The smoke is white!

67
00:10:32,916 --> 00:10:35,918
The thousands of faithful here
in St. Peter's Square...

68
00:10:36,003 --> 00:10:39,255
joyfully applaud the news.

69
