saying the smoke is black.

72
00:10:49,933 --> 00:10:54,020
The smoke, actually...

73
00:10:54,772 --> 00:10:57,899
Yes, the smoke is black.

74
00:10:57,941 --> 00:11:00,193
Yes, it's black, nothing doing.

75
00:11:00,319 --> 00:11:04,072
