can filter through to the outside.

78
00:11:15,084 --> 00:11:17,043
Aguilar.

79
00:11:18,671 --> 00:11:20,463
Gregori.

80
00:11:20,589 --> 00:11:22,340
Lucci.

81
00:11:24,843 --> 00:11:26,177
Bikila.

82
00:11:26,220 --> 00:11:29,347
Another black smoke signal.

83
