The cardinals in the Conclave still
haven't managed to elect a Pope.

84
00:11:33,686 --> 00:11:36,813
A second vote will be cast
this afternoon.

85
00:11:36,855 --> 00:11:41,609
We don't know if the favorites are
still Gregori, Aguilar and Bikila.

86
00:12:13,642 --> 00:12:14,254
Melville.

87
00:12:41,754 --> 00:12:43,379
Aguilar.

88
00:12:44,298 --> 00:12:44,910
Melville.

89
00:12:52,055 --> 00:12:53,639
Cevasco.

90
00:12:54,808 --> 00:12:55,420
Melville.

91
